# Stakeholder Analysis

## Project Title

Dealership Lead Management Transformation using Salesforce Automotive Cloud

## Purpose

The purpose of this stakeholder analysis is to identify all key stakeholders involved in the dealership lead management process, understand their business objectives, assess their influence on the project, and determine their requirements and expectations from the proposed Salesforce Automotive Cloud solution.

---

