# Conclusion

The success of the Dealership Lead Management Transformation project depends on effectively addressing stakeholder needs across sales, marketing, customer service, operations, and executive management. Continuous stakeholder engagement, requirement validation, and feedback collection will ensure successful implementation of the proposed Salesforce Automotive Cloud solution and maximize business value.
